COMANDO DE USO

-- Simulated System --


-- Real System --
1. We launch the ardrone driver:
	roslaunch vision ardrone_setup.launch

2. We launch the joy node, ardrone_teleop node (for the joystick) and the aruco_single node (for tag detection)
	roslaunch vision platform_detection_real.launch

3. Finally, we launch the platform_tracking_real node:
	roslaunch vision platform_tracking_real.launch